# Master Harvest Archive

This directory is the landing zone for the central markdown archives that feed the
Mapping-and-Inventory RAG ingestion engine.

- Drop `.md` / `.txt` archives (master harvest transmissions, knowledge graph exports,
  district scrolls, etc.) directly into this folder.
- The core ingestion scripts (`scripts/rag_ingest.py`) are wired to read from here
  by default when the legacy `master_intelligence_map.txt` is unavailable.
- Run `python ignite_hub_memory.py` from the repository root to trigger the central
  ingestion process against this directory.

This `.gitkeep` ensures the directory is tracked even when empty.
